a Exclusive: One of the world's bigge... a Exclusive: One of the world's biggest developers hunts for mega projects in Oakland, S.F. Next Story Prev Story 6 hrs ago Read more: Business Journal 
One of the world's largest real estate developers, Shanghai-based Greenland Holding Group, is in talks to invest and build in the Bay Area for the first time, the company's U.S. head told the San Francisco Business Times. Greenland's I-Fei Chang , who is overseeing $6 billion worth of development in the U.S., is looking for opportunities to park billions more.   Business Journal.
